      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is optimized by a factory variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The suspension retains its tactile feedback with refreshed bushings, while the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term internal engine health. This specimen offers a visceral, analog driving experience with the structural and mechanical integrity required for spirited performance.",
